59
00:04:26,534 --> 00:04:27,409
Nul.

60
00:04:32,039 --> 00:04:33,958
- Tu viens faire quoi ?
- Bosser.

61
00:04:34,250 --> 00:04:36,335
Comment ça, dans ce bureau ?

62
00:04:36,627 --> 00:04:39,839
